TextEng: Trial? What trial?
I'm the defense counsel for Rolgan.
I'll be going now.
Do you know why they were fighting?
What happened to your leg?
Anything else you can tell me?
You don't seem very impartial.
I get the feeling you're holding back on me.
What's wrong with your leg?
If I find out you're holding anything back, the pain won't only be in your leg!
Text: 뭔가 숨기는 게 있다는 걸 알게 되면, 다리만 아플 게 아닐 거야!

TextEng: I've got a few healing spells of my own. Maybe I can help.
Text: 내가 치유 주문 좀 알아. 도와줄 수 있을 것 같은데.

TextEng: I think you know something about Griff's death you aren't telling me.
Text: 그리프의 죽음에 대해 말 안 하는 뭔가를 알고 있는 것 같은데.

TextEng: Here you go, good as new. <StartCheck>[Use Minor Healing Spell]</Start>
Text: 자, 이제 새 것처럼 됐어. <StartCheck>[가벼운 치유 주문 사용]</Start>

TextEng: I changed my mind. I think I'll let you suffer.
Why you leg got ouchie?
Me go now.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Bad news. You wages got cut. You gotta give back 50 gold.
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 나쁜 소식이야. 너 월급 깎였어. 너 금화 50개 돌려줘야 해.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Bad news. Wages have been cut. You have to give back 50 gold from your salary.
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 나쁜 소식이에요. 월급이 깎였어요. 급여에서 금화 50개를 돌려줘야 해요.

TextEng: Give me you gold or me rip you sore leg right off!
Text: 나한테 금화 줘, 아니면 나 너 아픈 다리 뜯어낼 거야!

TextEng: Hand over your gold or I'll rip that injured leg right off!
Text: 금화 내놔, 아니면 그 다친 다리 뜯어버릴 거야!

TextEng: You all hurt, you keep gold.
Text: 너 다 다쳤어, 너 금화 가져.

TextEng: Tell you what, since you're injured I'll let you keep your wages.
That not me problem. You give gold now.
Text: 그거 내 문제 아니야. 너 금화 지금 줘.

TextEng: Not my problem. Just hand over the gold.
Text: 내 문제 아니야. 그냥 금화 내놔.

TextEng: What did happen that night with Griff?
Text: 그날 밤 그리프한테 무슨 일이 있었던 거야?
